---
// You can customize the content and add an image
---

<section class="bg-black text-white py-20 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image Side -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="aspect-square bg-gray-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Replace with actual image -->
          <img 
            src="/about-image.jpg" 
            alt="Playmakxrs Training" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content Side -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          About <span class="text-gold">Playmakxrs</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Sports have the power to bring us together, break down barriers, and transform lives. 
            At Playmakxrs, we believe in harnessing that power to develop not just better athletes, 
            but better people.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            With years of experience training athletes at every level, from youth programs to 
            professional competitors, we've developed a proven approach that combines technical 
            excellence with character development.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Our mission is simple: help every athlete we work with reach their full potential, 
            on and off the field.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <a 
          href="#contact" 
          class="inline-block mt-8 border-2 border-gold text-gold hover:bg-gold hover:text-black font-display font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-all duration-300"
        >
          Work With Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
